All Implemented Interfaces:
IBinarySearchTree<T,S>
public class AVLTree<T extends Comparable<T>,S extends AVLTreeNode<T>> extends BinarySearchRecursiveTree<T,S>
a self balancing binary search tree which maintains a height difference no greater than 1 between the 2 subtrees of a node. The height is the largest distance from a node to a descendant leaf. The implementation follows MIT opencourseware class 6.006 Unit 2.
